title: [Whistler's Pass, Grassy Field]
description: The mist turns to a dense fog here, obscuring the trail in the glow of reflected moonlight as it eddies throughout the area.  Thankfully, the trail is clear and somewhat straight as it continues its journey.  Linden trees line the path, their upper branches arching over the path itself.
